<font face="Serif" size="18">忘れていた</font>

77
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,320
<font face="Serif" size="18">来て姉妹たち</font>

78
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,120
<font face="Serif" size="18">この一杯目は</font>

79
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:59,960
<font face="Serif" size="18">私と元英さんの禁足解除を祝って</font>

80
